## Installation:

$ git clone git://github.com:soulston/dotvim.git ~/.vim

## Create sylinks:

$ ln -s ~/.vim/.vimrc ~/.vimrc
$ ln -s ~/.vim/.gvimrc ~/.gvimrc

## git Submmodules

After cloning the repo you need to fetch the submodules

$ cd ~/.vim
$ git submodule init
$ git submodule update

## Plugins

